        "created_at": "2025-02-08T15:57:37.756Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I found that the video sent in Signal chat is not clear, even when the media quality is set to high. It is even worse than many other chat software in this regard. This is very annoying. Can you add a video clarity adjustment function to allow sending clearer videos?<br>\n<div class=\"lightbox-wrapper\"><a class=\"lightbox\" href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/a/4/a4ffb77d88ef18d3f984f3e23f5afbcc98961784.jpeg\" data-download-href=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/a4ffb77d88ef18d3f984f3e23f5afbcc98961784\" title=\"IMG_1782\"><img src=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/a/4/a4ffb77d88ef18d3f984f3e23f5afbcc98961784_2_690x491.jpeg\" alt=\"IMG_1782\" data-base62-sha1=\"nxEaTI9EJMH83uRIoJZXIYISGjO\" width=\"690\" height=\"491\" srcset=\"https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/a/4/a4ffb77d88ef18d3f984f3e23f5afbcc98961784_2_690x491.jpeg, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/optimized/3X/a/4/a4ffb77d88ef18d3f984f3e23f5afbcc98961784_2_1035x736.jpeg 1.5x, https://community.signalusers.org/uploads/db3609/original/3X/a/4/a4ffb77d88ef18d3f984f3e23f5afbcc98961784.jpeg 2x\" data-dominant-color=\"EFEFEF\"><div class=\"meta\"><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-far-image svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#far-image\"></use></svg><span class=\"filename\">IMG_1782</span><span class=\"informations\">1170×834 51.9 KB</span><svg class=\"fa d-icon d-icon-discourse-expand svg-icon\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><use href=\"#discourse-expand\"></use></svg></div></a></div></p>",
